name: aircases
overview:
Aircase HongKong Technology Co., Limited, located in Shenzhen, China, mainly produces mobile phone accessories, such as protective shells, external batteries, leather cases, speakers and other accessories. Our factories cover approximately 6000sq meters locating in Shenzhen, the economic city of south China. Our company has a complete and scientific quality management system.

Aircases HongKong Technology Co.,Ltd. is equipped with the latest precision machines and inspection instrument, has about 500 skillful employees. we have engaged in the manufactory for many years, have rich experience in making the complex structure plastic molds, such as hot runner molds, overmolds ,rotational molds, unscrew molds, multi-cavity mold etc., we make plastic moulds for the common industries of auto, household, medical , office and electronic.

Certified by ISO9001-2008, we continually carry out activities of ISO and RoHS management system, which guarantee your satisfaction at our highest qualities and best services. We believe on-time delivery and competitive price with good quality and excellent service will help you to win the market all the time.

The honesty, products and high quality of Aircase HongKong Technology Co., Limited are well approved by customers. We welcome friends to visit our company for guidance and business negotiation. We hope to establish long-term strategic cooperation with the vast majority of customers for mutual development.
